## Color Palette and Healthcare Theming System

### Primary Color System

```css
:root {
  /* Primary Healthcare Colors */
  --hc-blue-primary: #23408e;      /* Trust, security, competence */
  --hc-blue-secondary: #385399;    /* Supporting actions */
  --hc-green-healing: #28a745;     /* Success, healthy status, healing */
  --hc-green-mint: #20c997;        /* Wellness, positive outcomes */
  
  /* Alert and Status Colors */
  --hc-red-critical: #dc3545;      /* Critical alerts, emergency status */
  --hc-yellow-warning: #ffc107;    /* Caution, attention needed */
